=== alert_recommendations ===

As per the SC200, it is recommended to assign these alerts these specific severities

--- Medium ---
> Unusual CPU utilization in a virtual machine
> Excessive number of failed login attempts to an application
> Anomalous outbound connections from a container instance

--- High ---
> Unauthorized access attempt to a database
> Suspicious file modification in a storage account
> Abnormal network traffic detected
> Unusual user accessed a key vault
> Log on from an unusual location
> Impossible travel activity
